node.text: For the latest installment of “Invite Only”, @hypebeastjp’s @yvkiabe linked up with multi-hyphenate Poggy to chat about his latest pick up, including the @adidasoriginals NMD S1, celebratory @newbalance 990, a bag by @larrysmith_official, and upcycled denim by @proletareart.

node.text: The highly-anticipated album is now set to release on August 15. The date was confirmed by an iTunes album preview page. The album was predicted to release following the end of ’Ye’s second listening event but to no surprise no album was released. Watch our latest episode of HBNN to get the “whoopity-scoop.”

node.text: Skateboarding made its debut at the summer Olympics in Tokyo and we took a look at some of the best moments, how its spotlighting streetwear, and how the addition of new sports is connecting with the younger audience.

node.text: The new album is named for West’s late mother, who passed away in 2007. While DONDA explores a wider range of genres than his previous album Jesus is King, it features some of the religious themes that West has pivoted to in his recent music. A partial tracklist posted by West ahead of the release listed titles like “Pure Souls” and “Keep My Spirit Alive.” The album will be available for purchase and streaming on July 23rd.

node.text: Founded by Jeff Bezos, space travel company Blue Origin completed its first passenger flight on July 20. The rocket, named New Shepard, carried Bezos and three other passengers more than 65-miles above Earth, just to the boundary of space, known as the Kármán line. Watch our latest episode of HBNN to learn more.

node.title: @jeffbezos Completes His First Flight into Space

node.text: @gucci unveils inaugural ‘Fashion Haul’ episode for its new web series in partnership with HYPEBEAST - bringing together prominent figures to break down the luxury house’s latest designs and exploring subcultures through the world of user-generated online streaming. node.text: Continuing to make sure that fans have something to celebrate whether they’re courtside or elsewhere, @oculus is partnering with HYPEBEAST News Network to share the top NBA-related news, keeping you up to date on all things basketball all season long. In this episode, we take a look at the new promo for ‘Space Jam: A New Legacy,’ starring LeBron James, in addition to the movie’s merchandise drops from Nike and Converse.

node.text:
Our first ever @hypegolf Invitational in Miami took place on May 13 and brought together the best in style, music, entertainment, food, and, of course, golf. Stay tuned for the next one in a city near you.
Thank you all who came out! @remi.god @manoloteachesgolf @mattjames919 @tjmizell @williemack3 @parishilinskigolf @janetgretzky @oooolajuwon @eastsidegolf @jabbawockeez @coach_rusty @haileyostrom @holein1trickshots @stephenmalbon @malbongolf @mvegapena @adriancolbert @earldreambig
#hypegolf #hypegolfinvitational

@hypebeaststyle: @asaprocky’s @awgenization and @nepenthes.official’s @needles_tokyo_official have joined forces for a new collection. node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: @supremenewyork just previewed its Fall/Winter 2021 collection and included in it is a "Wheat" iteration of the divisive Air Force 1 "Box Logo" which was originally introduced as part of the Spring/Summer 2020 collection in black and white. Often dubbed "lazy" or "boring", the Supreme x Nike Air Force 1 is an essential as it ultimately serves the same purpose Supreme’s universal Hanes boxers, socks, and tee. Hit the link in bio for our take on this collaboration.⁠
Photo: Supreme

node.text:
@hypebeastmusic: @champagnepapi recently showed appreciation for @richforever, even going as far as calling him the greatest rapper alive. Taking to his Instagram Story, Drake featured the Maybach Music founder and Smiley with the caption, “@richforever @thareal_smiley the greatest rapper alive met my favourite rapper alive.” Get the full scoop via the link in bio and let us know your thoughts below.⁠
Photo: Johnny Nunez/Getty Images

node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: @takahiromiyashitathesoloist has teamed up with @suicoke_official on a @vibram FiveFingers shoes release. Centered around a sleek black tone, the unique footwear silhouette is constructed of matching mesh and suede panels tied together with a traditional lace closure. Rounding out the design is a rugged rubber outsole that accents the separated toe design. Pick up a pair via Suicoke’s website now.⁠⁠
Photo: TAKAHIROMIYASHITATheSoloist/Suicoke

node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: @atmos_japan and @drmartensofficial have teamed up for a new take on the Tarik Zip Boot. Inspired by the sui generis visual style of anime, the boot is made of soft black velvet that is trimmed with smooth leather eyestays, collars and heel pieces. Other details include silver eyelets, criss-crossed red laces, a co-branded tongue badge, and a yellow heel tab. Get a pair via both brands’ websites on August 21 for $150 USD.⁠⁠
Photo: Dr. Martens

@hypebeastcarclub: Vintage car lovers can now own a fully electrified 1972 @ford Bronco for $380,000 USD. Crafted by @gatewaybronco, the newly revitalized Luxe-GT Bronco takes on its beautifully retro 1972 make but carries a modern 220kW electric motor capable of delivering a 0-60mph time of just under five seconds. ⁠Get a full look via the link in bio. ⁠⁠
Photo: Gateway Bronco

#hypeAF: An anonymous seller has put the tissue used by @leomessi during his @fcbarcelona departure press conference up for sale. Listed at $1 million USD, the price is based on the idea that it contains Messi’s “genetic material” which can be used to make a clone of the soccer star.⁠
Photo: Pau Barrena/Getty Images

@hypebeastmusic: Start your week with HYPEBEAST Sounds, our ongoing playlist that rotates through 50 of our editors’ current favorite tracks. Swipe to check out some of this week’s highlights and hit the link in bio for the rest. What are you listening to?⁠⁠ ⁠⁠

node.text:
@hypebeastcarclub: For our latest international edition of DRIVERS, we highlight South Korean rapper @gaekogeem and his immaculate 1988 @bmw 325i E30.⁠⁠ Gaeko's taste for the classic 3-series is refined, with OEM+ options helping to make the 30+ year-old convertible something special. M-Technic bits like the front and rear bumper and steering wheel keep things in-house, while the 17" @bbswheels RS wheels are a given and perhaps one of the most popular choices for modern classic Bimmers.⁠⁠ Swipe for a preview and hit the link in bio to read the HYPEBEAST Korea feature.⁠⁠
Photo: Seunghoon Jeong/@hypebeastkr

node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: Take an on-foot look at @maniere_usa's upcoming collaboration taking form in the Air Jordan 1 High. The shoe looks to bring its premium take to the classic silhouette boasting sail suede uppers paired with hits of burgundy along the snakeskin Swoosh, laces, wings logo, and outsole. Highlights include co-branding on the tongue as well as a hidden detail behind the ankle flaps with on of MJ's signature quotes: “You have to expect things of yourself before you can do them.” Expect these to arrive sometime in holiday 2021.⁠⁠
Photo: @yankeekicks

node.text:
#hypeAF: @nasa‘s latest Northrop Grumman Sygnus resupply mission carried a 3D regolith printer to the International Space Station. The Redwire Regolith Print project which converts moon dust particles into solid materials will work in conjunction with an existing ISS printer system, ManD, to test 3D printing as a technique for construction on future missions to the Moon and Mars.⁠
Photo: Redwire Regolith Print
